snippet.title: Dune: Awakening Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Rise from survival to dominance in Dune: Awakening, an Open World Survival MMO set on Arrakis.

Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1172710/Dune_Awakening/
Sign up for the Beta: https://dunegames.com/

Join us on Arrakis
Twitter: https://twitter.com/DuneAwakening
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DuneAwakening
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/duneawakening/
Discord: https://discord.gg/duneawakening
